      "content": "wait r u sure? i've had migraines for years and they get crazy bad sometimes. i'm also feeling super stressed lately and havent slept much. could it just be a massive migraine triggered by stress? i really dont want to go to the er if i dont have to, it's so expensive and i'm usually fine after some rest.",
