      "content": "i hear you but i'm just really scared to go. my friend had something similar once and it turned out to be a hemiplegic migraine and they didnt need a hospital. if i just take some extra strong ibuprofen and try to sleep it off for a few hours, would that be okay? like, if the drooping goes away when i wake up, i'll go then. it's probably just the tension though, right?",
